Instagram post by @noorie_rai, 15 August 2016 (Indian Independence Day). Image shows map of India with 3D text: 'I AM MUSLIM HINDU BUDDHIST SIKH CHRISTIAN JAIN'. Posted on Independence Day — a message of religious unity on the day of national unity. All religions emanating from the singular 'I AM.' Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Universal Consciousness — Satyuga has no religious divisions.